To implement role-based JWT authentication in Spring Boot (latest version ‚Äî Spring Boot 3.x with Spring Security 6.x), follow this full guide.

‚úÖ Features We Will Cover
JWT-based login (/login)

Generate and validate JWT tokens

Secure endpoints using roles (hasRole("ADMIN"), hasAuthority("ROLE_USER"))

Stateless authentication (no sessions)

Example roles: ROLE_ADMIN, ROLE_USER

